o Check password protected e-payslip
o Check leave and benefit entitlement balances
o Apply for leave, benefit and other requests
o Approve requests submitted by subordinates
• Communicate securely across the organization with enterprise-level encryption technologies.

• Share information with definable sharing scopes for team communication on news feed.
• Send text messages, images, videos, voice messages, location and contact to other employees in the company easily.
• Send secret messages that need a higher level of privacy to colleagues.
• Communicate and collaborate with other employees on any device, any time.
